				<td colspan="2"><span>DD procs.
<br />

<br />
I wouldn't go the lifetap route unless you plan on being Tank most of the times. Why lifetap for half the damage a DD proc does (EF ice DD proc is 760ap and 150 DMG. BB Lifetap proc is 1150ap for 75 tap) when you at 100% HPs or not holding agro since not being MA? However lifetaps would be sweet for melee soloing  <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-5.gif" border="0" alt="Wink" hspace="2" /></span></td>
			</tr><tr>
