				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Augment Suggestions<a name="33793"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Apr 9 04 10:51 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I like lifetaps because if I'm meleeing, I'm generally pulling too and that means I'll have a few HP to make up when I get the mob back to camp.  
<br />

<br />
If you're going the DD route, I recommend paying as much attention to the debuff part of the proc as the damage.  You'll end up doing more damage if your proc hits for full because of a debuff than if it's always hitting for half of a larger base DD.
<br />

<br />
My 2cp,</span></td>
