				<td colspan="2"><span>If you can afford the 75 pt DD, then you probably are grouping at a high enough level that you've got regen buffs.  Regen buffs + bard regen = 70+ regen/tick = same regen as the 75 dd.
<br />

<br />
Since most procs goes off twice per tick (with 305 dex) then yer adding about 20% regen.  If you rely on regen to heal up, 20% more may help.  But, I seriously doubt that in any reasonable group that you are relying on regen to heal you up if you are pulling.  Quiessence is your friend.
<br />

<br />
Go with DD.
