				<td colspan="2"><span>I don't like Lifetap aug ... in my opinion. At high levels mobs that hit you for 800-1200 a hit and you lifetap it for 75hp, not to mention it doesn't go off all the time. 
<br />

<br />
Well if you are a tank I can see perhaps you would say it will improve your tanking in the long run and that may be true but I would like to redirect.
<br />

<br />
120 dmg or 75dmg. When you think about it, its about defense or offense. And when you compare it, offense is a better choice because DPS is the way to go these days. By killing the mob a lot faster you save yourself from needing lifetaps however if you want to gain a little and give a little, lifetap does sound like a good choice.
<br />

<br />
But as a bard since we are not tanking most of the time, I say kill the mob faster please.
<br />

<br />
The main thing I am going at here is DPS, i know we don't do a whole lot of it but its better than nothing.
